{"tid":1394293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［心理輔導/解夢］發夢發到好絕望好攰既人入黎啦","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:33.000Z","uid":50286,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"667c05663c38df26171a0b460009a1d413592d52","tid":1394293,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNvjroG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNvjroG.png&h=5028cefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係外國做開心理輔導既 係最近一次恐怖襲擊我都有輔導受害人，家屬同埋其他受到影響既人<br />\n<br />\n見到大家係香港博曬命我都想出一分力<br />\n<br />\n我唔識用tg所以開左個instagram比大家做樹洞或者約個時間一對一心理輔導（Skype, FaceTime) <br />\n<br />\n我同大家保證所有野係絕對保密 如果冇你許可/consent所有野係絕對保密 絕對confidential <br />\n<br />\n有需要既話可以叫我證明我係外國同埋我做開輔導個d野 有做過防自殺training<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5iQx5K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5iQx5K.png&h=ec7ae350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我講你講既野全部都係發夢就得啦！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我會盡量覆 或者如果巴絲打淨係想舒發下都可以係依個post到覆 <br />\n<br />\n如果你好急想要同人講野可以話我知 我會盡快覆你 因為都有時差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFact check<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCo839H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCo839H.png&h=5f1cc26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: counsellinghk<br />\n<br />\n最後最後<br />\n如果你見到身邊既人好唔妥都可以叫佢地搵我傾下！"},{"pid":"f2cc207f9df05382710815d0665893bd84bf6a62","tid":1394293,"uid":205598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"0c667df92229566aca90fbe2f18ed466d1a0de53","tid":1394293,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2cc207f9df05382710815d0665893bd84bf6a62","tid":1394293,"uid":205598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,